ile, that detail isn't really lost. I'm also confirming the toolbox/ section only has doc/ and src/ listed in the source, and both are present in the knowledge file. For the Nablarch-dev-env.zip section, the key software versions (Eclipse 3.6 and Tomcat 6.0.32) are captured in the knowledge file, which covers the essential information.\n\nI'm satisfied this is a clean knowledge file with no significant gaps.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":23060,"cache_read_input_tokens":29807,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":23060,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4ac79c04-9ed1-426c-81ce-1720c2023fa7","uuid":"fd0e4697-d73c-4ccd-81ee-5bc3fde7be05"}
